I haven't enough data to say yes or no to your statement about DI and I was under the impression that final calculated damage values were rounded up rather than being just rounded. Just ran some quick checks on data that was posted in this thread  for Emperor Ssraeshza though and it appears you are correct. Damage is rounded to the nearest integer after being calculated.<br>
<br>
